<lb n="0922b24" ed="T"/>彌娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十四</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>摩舍迦<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0922b25" ed="T"/>喃<note place="inline">引十五</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>莽酤拏<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引十六</note>薩哩
